vene Hydrance Intense Hydrating Serum</h3>\r\n                    <h4 class=\"mt-3\">A glass of water for your skin</h4>\r\n                    <div class=\"product-right\" style=\"float:right; width:200px; text-align: center; margin-left: 25px\">\r\n                        <a\r\n                        href=\"https://www.caretobeauty.com/avene-hydrance-intense-hydrating-serum-30ml/\"\r\n                        >\r\n                        <img\r\n                            height=\"200px\"\r\n                            class=\"size-thumbnail lazyloaded\"\r\n                            src=\"https://static.beautytocare.com/media/catalog/product/a/v/avene-hydrance-intense-hydrating-serum-30ml_2.jpg\"\r\n                            data-src=\"https://static.beautytocare.com/media/catalog/product/a/v/avene-hydrance-intense-hydrating-serum-30ml_2.jpg\"\r\n                            alt=\"Avene Hydrance Intense Hydrating Serum 30ml\"\r\n                            />\r\n                        <p class=\"mt-3\">Avene Hydrance Intense Hydrating Serum</p>\r\n                        <p>\r\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-primary text-light px-4\">\r\n                            Buy Now\r\n                            </button>\r\n                        </p>\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <p>\r\n                        <a\r\n                            href=\"https://www.caretobeauty.com/avene-hydrance-intense-hydrating-serum-30ml/\"\r\n                            ></a>\r\n                        </p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>\r\n                        Infused with <strong>Avene</strong> thermal spring water,\r\n                        <strong>Avene Hydrance Intense Hydrating Serum</strong> provides the\r\n                        skin with a boost of hydration, leaving the skin plump and supple.\r\n                        The light serum texture is easily absorbed and sinks comfortably\r\n                        into the skin, providing instant relief from dryness and leaving the\r\n                        skin fresh, luminous, and radiant throughout the day.\r\n                    </p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>\r\n                    <hr />\r\n                    <p>\r\n                        Well, now that you\'ve seen our selection of the best\r\n                        <strong>Avene</strong> products out there, we hope you\'ve found the\r\n                        right one for you. Looking for something else? Then don\'t hesitate\r\n                        to\r\n                        <a href=\"https://www.caretobeauty.com/avene/\">browse the full <strong>Avene</strong> skincare range here</a>.\r\n                    </p><br><br>\r\n                </div>', '2022-04-01', '5:20 pm', '<div class=\"headings\">             <a href=\"#intro\" id=\"heading\" style=\"display: block !important; margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 2rem;\">Introduction</a>             <a href=\"#moist\" id=\"heading\" style=\"display: block !important; margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 2rem;\">SOS Moisturizer</a>             <a href=\"#cleanse\" id=\"heading\" style=\"display: block !important; margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 2rem;\">Cleansing Gel</a>             <a href=\"#moist2\" id=\"heading\" style=\"display: block !important; margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 2rem;\">A.D. Moisturizer</a>             <a href=\"#cream\" id=\"heading\" style=\"display: block !important; margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 2rem;\">Protective Cream</a>             <a href=\"#moist3\" id=\"heading\" style=\"display: block !important; margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 2rem;\">Daily Moisturizer</a>             <a href=\"#sun\" id=\"heading\" style=\"display: block !important; margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 2rem;\">Sunscreen</a>             <a href=\"#cream2\" id=\"heading\" style=\"display: block !important; margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 2rem;\">Antirougeurs Cream</a>             <a href=\"#serum\" id=\"heading\" style=\"display: block !important; margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 2rem;\">Serum</a>         </div>'),
